{"tid":469511,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"福布斯評30 歲以下遊戲界大人物，《LOL》Bjergsen 、HotshotGG 入選","createTime":"2017-11-15T11:28:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T19:25:08.000Z","uid":608,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"ee8a98993f1895229650c370228eb52d70840a2e","tid":469511,"uid":608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:28:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/api/res/1.2/XsuVVwIvJBMOrFthH1_5_A--/YXBwaWQ9ZXNwb3J0O3NtPTE7dz04ODA-/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/c927b0200d2f4d791c018cfa8e11a2e3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Flo%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FXsuVVwIvJBMOrFthH1_5_A--%2FYXBwaWQ9ZXNwb3J0O3NtPTE7dz04ODA-%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fc927b0200d2f4d791c018cfa8e11a2e3&h=3da79fa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/api/res/1.2/D7C4n.DD3yxFam8oP9wa4Q--/YXBwaWQ9ZXNwb3J0O3NtPTE7dz04ODA-/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/4b593654100de2dd767ef3f78752231e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Flo%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FD7C4n.DD3yxFam8oP9wa4Q--%2FYXBwaWQ9ZXNwb3J0O3NtPTE7dz04ODA-%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F4b593654100de2dd767ef3f78752231e&h=033c6605&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n福布斯每年經常都會評選各個職業領域的風雲人物，今年也不例外，近期釋出的其中一份名單「30 歲以下的遊戲界代表人物」評比中，令人眼睛為之一亮的就有《英雄聯盟》的 Bjergsen 、HotshotGG 以及 Youtube 的全球電競頭頭 Lester Chen 等人。<br />\n<br />\nBjergsen 為北美知名戰隊 Team SoloMid （TSM）的中路選手，曾多次帶領隊伍奪下北美賽區的冠軍，也被許多玩家認為是北美最強的《英雄聯盟》選手，目前才 21 歲的他，未來肯定能夠更加發光發熱。而另一名入選的 HotshotGG 曾為北美老牌隊伍 Counter Logic（CLG） 的招牌選手，在 WCG 2010 率隊奪下四項冠軍，許多人認為他是世界最具知名度的《英雄聯盟》人物，也是《英雄聯盟》現在能夠那麼盛行的推手之一。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外入選的還有在 Youtube 管理全球電競內容的總監 Lester Chen ，不僅為 Youtube 促成多項賽事轉播如：ESL Pro League 、 FACEIT&rsquo;s Esports Championship Series 等，也是今年 Youtube 《英雄聯盟》世界冠軍賽 VR 4K 體驗幕後推手。其他入選的在遊戲界也都是非常厲害的人物，不知道哪一天有沒有機會看到台灣人出現在名單上呢？讓我們拭目以待囉！<br />\n<br />\n轉:<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/tjAFo2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FtjAFo2&d=ldFL%2FGoPYvM%2FPjc8ZZXggMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=979e8cbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/tjAFo2</a><br />\nLIST:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/30-under-30/2018/games/#187b4cd41aeb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2F30-under-30%2F2018%2Fgames%2F%23187b4cd41aeb&d=ldFL%2FGoPYvM%2FPjc8ZZXggMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=e58a3024\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.forbes.com/30-under-30/2018/games/#187b4cd41aeb</a>"},{"pid":"2e31a1ef2d15d4de00412f0e7f1e923b879f9eab","tid":469511,"uid":608,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:31:29.000Z","msg":"undertale製作者toby fox都有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20cc10c8643b1688601fc078b80de9bb4c206be","tid":469511,"uid":52942,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T11:32:17.000Z","msg":"hsgg真係lol傳奇，但係佢唔屌人之後就唔好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39d7bce1ea41104616ad1cb0e7618193f7c065f","tid":469511,"uid":7140,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T12:00:27.000Z","msg":"Hsgg nid<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49bd32d9e01a46c1359c8f2d3a322702880ced3c","tid":469511,"uid":17678,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T12:02:08.000Z","msg":"冇當時hsgg 應該冇今日既lol"},{"pid":"c00e71570298bbf989e47974e5cf452ed7f5d0cd","tid":469511,"uid":19305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T12:05:03.000Z","msg":"神手貴呢？"},{"pid":"0e632c18a6bdadb6f333826d1b7bf8b23f2129a9","tid":469511,"uid":77355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T12:06:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>神手貴呢？</blockquote><br />\n<img sr